These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: soccer, handball, ice-hockey, lacrosse, cycling, snowboarding
The people have 6 different hobbies: drawing, writing, hiking, sudoku, video-games, board-games
 1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 2. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
 3. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
 4. the person who's hobby is board-games is not to the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##8
 5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##5
 6. the person who's hobby is video-games is somewhere between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who's sport is snowboarding##7
 7. the person who's sport is soccer is not to the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##8
 8. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
 9. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
10. the person who's hobby is drawing is not to the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##8
11. the person who's hobby is video-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5
12. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
13. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
14. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere between the person who's hobby is writing and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##7
15. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
16. the person who's sport is cycling is not the person who's hobby is sudoku##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |   4   |       5        |   6   |
| Sport           | lacrosse | handball | soccer | cycling | snowboarding | ice-hockey |
| Hobby   | drawing | hiking    | writing  | video-games  | sudoku            | board-games  |

