.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-2::.
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: cricket, skiing, biathlon, weightlifting, basketball, tennis
6 different games are played: go, domino, mah-jongg, poker, snooker, backgammon
 1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not the person playing backgammon##6
 2. the person playing backgammon is in an even position##4
 3. the person playing snooker is not to the right of the person playing poker##8
 4. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person playing backgammon is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person playing domino##2
 6. the person playing go is somewhere to the right of the person playing mah-jongg##5
 7. the person playing poker is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##5
 8. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
 9. the person who's sport is skiing is not the person playing poker##6
10. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left or far right##3
11. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the left of the person playing mah-jongg##8
12. the person playing backgammon is not to the right of the person who's sport is basketball##8
13. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
14. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person playing domino##1
15. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |      3       |   4    |    5    |    6    |
| Sport   | biathlon | tennis | skiing | basketball | weightlifting | cricket |
| Game     | mah-jongg  | go  | domino         | backgammon | snooker    | poker   |

