.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-3::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, milk, water, hot-chocolate, mirinda
The people use 6 different means of transport: motorbike, train, roller, jet-ski, trike, airplane
 1. the person driving the train is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5
 2. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person driving the train##5
 3. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
 4. the person driving the roller is not to the left of the person drinking juice##8
 5. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the person driving the airplane##5
 6. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
 7. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the right of the person drinking milk##5
 8. the person drinking water is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
 9. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking milk##5
10. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far right##1
11. the person driving the airplane is somewhere between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person driving the roller##7
12. the person driving the train is somewhere to the left of the person driving the roller##5
13. the person drinking mirinda is between the person driving the trike and the person driving the airplane##2
14. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking water##1
15. the person driving the roller is somewhere between the person driving the airplane and the person drinking iced-tea##7
16. the person driving the trike is not to the left of the person driving the trike##8
17. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the right of the person driving the trike##5
18. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person driving the train##1
19. the person driving the roller is not the person drinking iced-tea##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |       4       |     5     |    6     |
