 7. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
 8. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the left of the person playing mah-jongg##8
 9. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is sailing##5
