12. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
13. the person driving the taxi is on the far left or far right##3
14. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere between the person traveling to venice and the person driving the bus##7
15. the person traveling to venice is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |   3    |    4     |     5      |      6      |
| City   | venice | hannover | liverpool | miami   | san-francisco    | nizza |
| Transport   | boat | subway      | helicopter | van | bus | taxi  |

